<h3 class="js-sr-av">Pregunta</h3>
<div id="taquestion58_287" class="block question iDevice_content">
<p><b>Los estantes del medio del frigorífico se encuentran a una temperatura de:</b></p>
</div>
<div class="iDevice_answers">
<h4 class="js-sr-av">Respuestas</h4>
<div class="iDevice_answer">
<p class="iDevice_answer-field js-required">
<label for="i58_290" class="sr-av"><a href="#answer-58_290">Opción 1</a></label><input type="radio" name="option58_287" id="i58_290" onclick="getFeedback(0,3,'58_287','multi')"/>
</p>
<div class="iDevice_answer-content" id="answer-58_290"><a name="answer-58_290"></a>
<div id="taans58_290" class="block iDevice_content">
<p>Entre 0 y 2º C</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="iDevice_answer">
<p class="iDevice_answer-field js-required">
<label for="i58_293" class="sr-av"><a href="#answer-58_293">Opción 2</a></label><input type="radio" name="option58_287" id="i58_293" onclick="getFeedback(1,3,'58_287','multi')"/>
</p>
<div class="iDevice_answer-content" id="answer-58_293"><a name="answer-58_293"></a>
<div id="taans58_293" class="block iDevice_content">
<p>Entre 4 y 8º C.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="iDevice_answer">
<p class="iDevice_answer-field js-required">
<label for="i58_296" class="sr-av"><a href="#answer-58_296">Opción 3</a></label><input type="radio" name="option58_287" id="i58_296" onclick="getFeedback(2,3,'58_287','multi')"/>
</p>
<div class="iDevice_answer-content" id="answer-58_296"><a name="answer-58_296"></a>
<div id="taans58_296" class="block iDevice_content">
<p>Entre 8 y 10 º C.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
